data.description: This stunning property not only boasts a contemporary design but also offers a unique advantage, an assumable FHA loan with a remarkably low 3.125% interest rate. Imagine the financial benefit of securing a mortgage at this rate in today's market! Built in 2021, this Smart Home is a testament to modern living. With 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a spacious 3-car garage, it provides ample space for comfort and convenience. The interior is adorned with stylish features, including white kitchen cabinets, granite countertops throughout, high herringbone backsplash, walk-in pantry, and elegant engineered hardwood floors throughout the first floor. The heart of the home is accentuated by a gas fireplace, the kitchen comes equipped with stainless steel gas appliances, and high ceilings throughout add an airy and open feel. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, complete with an ensuite featuring a soaking tub and a perfect oasis for relaxation. Additional upgrades include a gazebo and hot tub along with its upgraded landscaping, creating a serene outdoor space for you to enjoy. Do not miss out on this exceptional opportunity to make this house your new home!
